The major Devops process includes 

1. Continous development: This is the proces whereby product development is being iterated and continously made better for customers. 

2. Continous iteration: The whole process is  continously iterated by both devellopment and operations to make sure that glitches and bugs are being captured early. 

3. Continous testing: Software testing is mostly automated and this allows product to be easily tested when new 

4. Monitoring, Feedback, Delivery: These are some of the major process that has to be continually iterated in devOps
